These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, collecting
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, mauve
1. the person who likes red is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes mauve is the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | collecting | card-games |
| Color     | mauve    | red   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
House: victorian, modern
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
2. the modern house is on the left of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| House   | modern | victorian        |
| Sport      | sailing  | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
2 different games are played: snooker, canasta
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, turkish
1. the canadian is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Game   | canasta    | snooker |
| Nationality   | canadian | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, car
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person driving the car is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | 7up      | lemonade |
| Transport       | ship | car    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, d&b
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, polish
1. the dutch is in an even position##4
2. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Music-Genre           | r&b | d&b |
| Nationality   | polish    | dutch         |

