The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, volleyball
1. the person traveling to venice is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| City   | venice | colone   |
| Sport         | skiing | volleyball |

