.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, rowing
2 different pets are kept: goat, turtle
1. the person who's sport is surfing is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |   2    |
| Sport   | surfing | rowing  |
| Pet   | goat      | turtle |

 